CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 24, 1959, pg. 1 reads: "Death Pyre - Seeking safety under a second-floor bed, the three young Dupree children died as flames slid to the first floor (shown by arrow)- Harris Photos."image published by Pittsburgh Courier with graphic addition.
